## ENTITY MAP

There are four distinct layers. Do not collapse them.

| Layer | Name | What It Is |
|---|---|---|
| **Creator** | E.I. Werner | The person and public identity. Name on the door. |
| **Show** | Make Myth | The livestream format. Fantasy worldbuilding in public. |
| **Community** | The Outside Inn | The room. Discord + Fourthwall memberships. |
| **Company** | Outside Inn Studios, LLC | The legal and operational entity behind all of it. |

Separation is intentional and load-bearing. Do not conflate these in copy, strategy, or structure.

