## COMMUNITY & MEMBERSHIP

Everything runs through **Fourthwall**. Discord is the lobby.

The pricing carries **base-7 DNA** from the cosmology (septimal numeral system). This is intentional throughout — prices, discounts, badge numbers, all divisible by 7.

| Tier | Price | What They Are |
|---|---|---|
| **Lobby** | Free | General Discord access + art wallpapers |
| **Innsider** | $7.77/mo | The community tier. Pull up a stool. Discord channel, 14% merch discount, stream vote, monthly patron livestream, rolling credits. Founding badge: first 777, numbered, permanent. |
| **Innkeep** | $21.21/mo | The inner circle. The back table. Everything in Innsider + Innkeep Discord, Signal group with Evan, 21% merch discount, writing review after 7 consecutive months. Founding badge: first 77, numbered, permanent. |

**Credit roll:** All paid members roll in video/stream credits in join order. Innkeeps are visually distinct from Innsiders — design-level, not loud.

**Growth funnel (sequenced, not simultaneous):**
1. Deputize the homies — founding members as culture co-owners
2. Warm network — personal outreach, LinkedIn underrated
3. Vertical clips — the scale lever, activates once streams are worth clipping

